117
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:09,480
No problem.

118
00:08:14,120 --> 00:08:16,790
[Flourishing Hope Law Firm]

119
00:08:23,920 --> 00:08:25,470
Dad.

120
00:08:30,020 --> 00:08:32,930
A'Shou, are you still as motivated as before?

121
00:08:32,930 --> 00:08:35,720
Only when dealing with divorce cases.

122
00:08:35,720 --> 00:08:37,540
I help others get out of the abyss of their misery.

123
00:08:37,540 --> 00:08:39,840
It's a charitable deed.

124
00:08:39,840 --> 00:08:42,170
If it's such a charitable deed, then you won't need to be collecting a fee. Right?

125
00:08:42,170 --> 00:08:44,150
You really have no sense of humor.

126
00:08:44,150 --> 00:08:46,000
All of our cases need to be taken seriously.

127
00:08:46,000 --> 00:08:48,880
All right, all right. You are the most genuine out of us all.

128
00:08:50,020 --> 00:08:51,580
