133
00:09:11,870 --> 00:09:14,310
- Hello, are you Ms. Ke Yunxi?
- Yes.

134
00:09:14,310 --> 00:09:17,480
- My name is Mr. Fu. This way, please.
- Thank you.

135
00:09:18,140 --> 00:09:20,670
