140
00:09:40,180 --> 00:09:42,970
He seems to have a lot of experience in this area.

141
00:09:42,970 --> 00:09:44,250
I understand your concerns.

142
00:09:44,250 --> 00:09:48,410
However, even the best lawyers are unable to do much when a law has been clearly violated.

143
00:09:48,410 --> 00:09:50,770
