144
00:09:50,770 --> 00:09:53,650
I wanted to ask, do you two have any children?

145
00:09:53,650 --> 00:09:55,470
If you don't have any children,

146
00:09:55,470 --> 00:09:57,940
then you won't have to deal with anything related to parental custody.

147
00:09:57,940 --> 00:10:01,030
The next steps are to apply for a protection order and petition for divorce.

148
00:10:01,030 --> 00:10:04,790
So I want to explain that these two matters will need to be heard before a judge, separately.

149
00:10:04,790 --> 00:10:07,260
