152
00:10:12,100 --> 00:10:14,340
- Hello?
- Hello, Mr. Qi.

153
00:10:14,340 --> 00:10:16,360
This is Lawyer Zheng. I just spoke with you over the phone.

154
00:10:16,360 --> 00:10:19,920
I do apologize, but I won't be able to fulfill your request.

155
00:10:19,920 --> 00:10:22,320
What's going on? Did you not say yesterday that you would be able to work with me?

156
00:10:22,320 --> 00:10:24,210
