210
00:13:53,330 --> 00:13:55,930
Just change the music.

211
00:13:58,690 --> 00:14:00,780
What's up?

212
00:14:00,780 --> 00:14:03,740
When did you start listening to jazz?

213
00:14:03,740 --> 00:14:07,120
Is it all to grab the attention of the beautiful bar manager?

214
00:14:07,120 --> 00:14:09,770
