255
00:17:37,940 --> 00:17:39,990
Hello, Lawyer Fu.

256
00:17:39,990 --> 00:17:43,510
Do you often deal with scary cases?

257
00:17:43,510 --> 00:17:46,030
Have you ever dealt with a murder case before?

258
00:17:46,030 --> 00:17:49,000
