259
00:17:50,200 --> 00:17:52,970
So what do you do with your free time then?

260
00:17:52,970 --> 00:17:56,890
Do you like sweets? I make desserts.

261
00:17:57,990 --> 00:18:01,020
For example, I like lemon pie,

262
00:18:01,020 --> 00:18:05,340
chocolate pie, and blueberry pie. What about you?

263
00:18:05,340 --> 00:18:07,830
I'm sorry, I just remembered that I still have something to take care of at work.

264
00:18:07,830 --> 00:18:09,650
I've got to get going.

265
00:18:09,650 --> 00:18:11,670
- You want to leave?
- Yes.

266
00:18:11,670 --> 00:18:13,520
It was really nice to meet you.

267
00:18:13,520 --> 00:18:15,920
It was nice to meet you, too.

268
00:18:15,920 --> 00:18:20,490
Do you like to travel? I really like traveling to Europe.

269
00:18:20,490 --> 00:18:21,950
- Hello.
- Hello.

270
00:18:21,950 --> 00:18:26,540
I'm sorry. We have something we need to deal with at work and we must get going.

271
00:18:26,540 --> 00:18:28,360
Oh, that was really fast.

272
00:18:28,360 --> 00:18:31,240
But I still want to get to know Mr. Gong better.

273
00:18:31,240 --> 00:18:33,400
I'm sorry, it was really nice to meet you.

274
00:18:33,400 --> 00:18:35,140
Can I add you on Line?

275
00:18:35,140 --> 00:18:37,790
He left his phone in the car.

276
00:18:37,790 --> 00:18:41,340
You can download a dating app, you'll have many options there.

277
00:18:41,340 --> 00:18:43,310
Goodbye!

278
00:18:43,310 --> 00:18:45,320
I never thought you would have to experience this, too.

279
00:18:45,320 --> 00:18:47,660
I never thought that Uncle Wang would also try to set you up.

280
00:18:47,660 --> 00:18:50,510
I'm sure 80% of them have been influenced by my dad.

281
00:18:50,510 --> 00:18:53,000
We have to continue to meet even more of them this afternoon.

282
00:18:53,000 --> 00:18:54,360
I'm more tired than when I go to court.

283
00:18:54,360 --> 00:18:57,140
It seems that Lawyer Fu is also a hard nut to crack.

284
00:18:57,140 --> 00:19:00,880
What do you think? Do you want to try out my plan?

285
00:19:01,770 --> 00:19:03,490
What plan?

286
00:19:03,490 --> 00:19:07,230
We need to see if you can fit into the script.

287
00:19:09,960 --> 00:19:13,670
I'm calling from the front lines of the battlefield. Xue Qing, are you there?

288
00:19:13,670 --> 00:19:18,050
I'm here! Brother Ligong, this is the game plan for the blind date operation.

289
00:19:18,990 --> 00:19:20,790
What is this?

290
00:19:22,710 --> 00:19:25,250
So you don't usually take these blind dates seriously?

291
00:19:25,250 --> 00:19:28,070
This kind of attitude and arrangement towards marriage doesn't suit me.

292
00:19:28,070 --> 00:19:31,530
I'd just get divorced very soon thereafter.

293
00:19:31,530 --> 00:19:33,370
Why do I have so many pages, and you only have one?

294
00:19:33,370 --> 00:19:35,660
Don't worry, Brother Ligong.

295
00:19:38,050 --> 00:19:40,000
With a great actor,

296
00:19:40,000 --> 00:19:42,600
one only needs to give him an outline.

297
00:19:42,600 --> 00:19:47,370
He can create an unlimited amount of lines and content.

298
00:19:47,370 --> 00:19:51,750
Hey, rookie. This is your first time in this role.

299
00:19:53,510 --> 00:19:56,590
When you don't know how to act, I would recommend

300
00:19:56,590 --> 00:19:58,620
that you read the script carefully

301
00:19:58,620 --> 00:20:00,520
and don't question the screenwriter.

302
00:20:00,520 --> 00:20:03,460
Follow the lines and instructions written above.

303
00:20:03,460 --> 00:20:05,400
As long as you do that, you'll be great!

304
00:20:06,050 --> 00:20:09,070
So you do this stuff all the time?

305
00:20:09,070 --> 00:20:10,770
Call me "Director".

306
00:20:10,770 --> 00:20:12,880
Wait! Am I not the director?

307
00:20:13,900 --> 00:20:16,790
