308
00:20:16,790 --> 00:20:20,830
Konstantin Stanislavski in his book "An Actor Prepares," mentions

309
00:20:20,830 --> 00:20:23,690
that actors have to be like soldiers.

310
00:20:23,690 --> 00:20:26,900
They must be resolute and disciplined.

311
00:20:28,370 --> 00:20:32,070
Don't worry, leave it all to me.

312
00:20:32,070 --> 00:20:36,790
Set the scene! And action!

313
00:20:36,790 --> 00:20:39,390
Hello, my name is Fu Ligong.

314
00:20:39,390 --> 00:20:43,090
I'm currently a lawyer at Flourishing Hope Law Firm.

315
00:20:43,840 --> 00:20:46,730
I'm sorry, this is my first blind date.

316
00:20:46,730 --> 00:20:50,400
I've never dated anyone before.

317
00:20:50,400 --> 00:20:52,960
Don't look at me! I don't dare to look straight at a woman!

318
00:20:52,960 --> 00:20:55,820
I'm the director, so I'll call "cut."

319
00:21:05,400 --> 00:21:08,390
There's something I need to tell you as well.

320
00:21:08,400 --> 00:21:12,200
I'm a boring person. I don't leave my house to do anything except work.

321
00:21:12,280 --> 00:21:15,840
My biggest interest is playing jigsaw puzzles at home.

322
00:21:16,810 --> 00:21:18,940
Excuse me.

323
00:21:18,940 --> 00:21:23,800
